formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
(1) We have relied on financial statements provided by promoter of the project while issuing Form 3.
(2) As per the act and regulation, it is mandatory to execute agreement for sale for the units before  receiving amount more than 10 % of the unit consideration amount and report date of AFS to GUJRERA. 
(3) As per Form 3 it is required to report unit wise encumbrance status at the reporting date. We would like to state that we have obtained  letter from promoter regarding unit wise status of encumbrance for each unit and relied on the same while reporting unit wise status of encumbrance.
(4) As Interest Cost Decrease As Compare to Previous Quarter, We want to Clarify That One Party To Whom Interest Amount Paid Cheque Given but the Same was not Cleared till Now Hence the Amount Paid is now Considered as Outstanding for Payment and Shown as Outstanding and Not Paid
(5) Promoter has made application For Society Registration however Society Registration Certificate is not received Till date So, we have attached herewith Application Letter.
